---
title: One Pot Spaghetti
source: https://www.instagram.com/reel/Cy4Lr-0pld3/
tags: dinner
---

In a #large pot{}, cook @Italian sausage{1%lb} over medium-high heat, breaking it up, until browned. Add @minced onion{1%tbsp}, @dried basil{1%tbsp}, @salt{}, @pepper{}, and @garlic powder{} and stir to combine.

Add @San Marzano whole peeled tomatoes{1%28-oz can}, @chicken broth{32%oz}, @heavy cream{1%cup}, and @spaghetti{1%lb} (broken in half if needed to fit). Bring to a boil, then reduce to a simmer, cover, and cook ~{20-25%minutes} until pasta is tender and sauce has thickened. Serve immediately.
